properties.description: 2016 Extended Orthophotos, Moldova, Executed by Primul Meridian SRL, scale 1:5000, 20cm, precision 0.5m, true colors, covers practically the entire territory of the Republic of Moldova, except some areas from the east part of Moldova,compared to original 2016 Ortophotos, these are extended with about 2-5 km at the boundaries.
